data.description: THIS 2 STORY MORNINGSIDE GEM BOAST OVERSIZED SWIMMING POOL, 2 KITCHENS, 2 UTILITY ROOMS AND 2 LIVING AREAS! COMPLETELY REMODELED UPSTAIRS AND DOWNSTAIRS. STUNNING STAIRCASE AS YOU STEP INTO THIS HOME THAT IS SET UP FOR 2 FAMILIES OR AIR B&B. UPSTAIRS HAS 2 BEDROOM, BONUS ROOM THAT COULD BE 5TH BEDROOM, FULL BATHROOM COMPLETELY REMODELED WITH BEAUTIFUL SHOWER AND VANITY, BRAND NEW UTILITY ROOM AND SPIRAL STAIRCASE THAT GOES DOWN TO ITS OWN COMPLETE KITCHEN AND 1/2 BATH AND SEPERATE ACCESS TO OUTSIDE! PLENTY OF SPACE TO ENTERTAIN BY THE SWIMMING POOL AND SPACIOUS PATIO AREA!  NEW FLOORING, WINDOWS, LIGHTING, BATHROOMS HAVE ALL BEEN REMODELED WITH 5X6 WALK-IN SHOWER IN PRIMARY BATH WITH SOAKER TUB. COMPLETE LIST OF DETAILED UPDATES AVAILABLE!! THIS IS A ONE OF A KIND MUST SEE!
